disapprove of cocktails in Babylon.

53
00:07:07,647 --> 00:07:10,398
Is this happiness?

54
00:07:10,566 --> 00:07:12,855
Is this perfection?

55
00:07:14,528 --> 00:07:21,610
As you are now, we once were.
