99
00:11:06,468 --> 00:11:11,843
- 'Yes, but apart from that.'
- 'Oooh! Ain't he bold!'

100
00:11:12,016 --> 00:11:15,432
(Davies) But the law proscribed
and was anything but tolerant.

101
00:11:15,603 --> 00:11:17,429
As when, contemporaneously,

102
00:11:17,605 --> 00:11:19,811
