spent dreaming in the sun.

154
00:15:14,550 --> 00:15:18,168
Between joy and consolation,
no easy path.

155
00:15:18,345 --> 00:15:21,050
Some flights of fancy,
some colour.

156
00:15:21,223 --> 00:15:24,473
Glorious old Hollywood;
small, comic England.

157
00:15:24,643 --> 00:15:26,221
Black and white.

158
00:15:26,979 --> 00:15:30,928
Between loving and hating,
the real journey starts.

159
00:15:31,108 --> 00:15:34,062
Let go the latter, embrace the former,

160
00:15:34,236 --> 00:15:37,771
then fall to heaven on a gentle smile.

161
00:15:39,533 --> 00:15:43,613
Between waking and sleeping,
the earth resumes its turn.

162
00:15:44,163 --> 00:15:46,914
The soft light fills the room,

163
00:15:47,082 --> 00:15:50,451
the nightly demons perish from the bed,

164
00:15:50,627 --> 00:15:54,376
and all humanity braves another day.

